Запрос 1 — все тендеры для конкретной транзакции (без фильтра по workstationid):

SELECT retailstoreid, workstationid, transactionsequencenumber,
       tendertypecode, tendersequencenumber, tenderamount, load_ts_xml
FROM ice_baby.core_flow_ing_raw.raw_bptender
WHERE retailstoreid = '34HG'
  AND transactionsequencenumber = '100000000001805652'
ORDER BY load_ts_xml, tendertypecode, tenderamount

